      <h2 class="heading text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-foreground mb-4">
        You Already Know It Matters
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto pb-1.5" style="font-family: 'Space Mono', 'Courier Prime', monospace;">
        You've been watching the shift for months. Reading about it. Thinking about it. The only thing separating you from the people already using AI to build leverage isn't intelligenceâ€”it's the decision to stop observing and start operating. The brain isn't the limitation. The hesitation is.
